gov.sandia.cognition.math.matrix.custom

Class NativeBlasHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.sandia.cognition.math.matrix.custom.NativeBlasHandler

  • @PublicationReference(author="Jeshua",
                      title="Netlib and Java",
                      type=WebPage,
                      year=2013,
                      url="http://www.jeshua.me/content/code/NetlibTest.java")
public class NativeBlasHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides a uniform interface between working with a native-coded BLAS package or the jBLAS package. This code was begun from an example found at http://www.jeshua.me/content/code/NetlibTest.java but modified for our purposes.
    Since:
    3.4.3
    Author:
    Jeremy D. Wendt
